summary: This is an email from an FBI agent forwarding additional documents that have been serialized, including interview reports and ten yearbooks received from the FBI West Palm Beach Resident Agency. It appears to be part of ongoing evidence collection in the Epstein investigation.
locations: FBI West Palm Beach Resident Agency
keyFacts: Additional documents were serialized and forwarded on January 13, 2021.
The documents include interview reports and ten yearbooks.
The yearbooks were received from the FBI West Palm Beach Resident Agency.
This email indicates ongoing evidence collection in the Epstein investigation.
